OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1781887673
OL,3,CJo Cox told friends 'let him hurt me'
OL,4,Cas they tried to stop killer
OL,6,FTwo friends have recalled how the MP
OL,7,FJo Cox told them "let him hurt me" as
OL,8,Fthey tried in vain to prevent her
OL,9,Fmurder at the hands of a far right
OL,10,Fextremist.
OL,12,FMother-of-two Mrs Cox died after being
OL,13,Fshot and stabbed by neo-Nazi Thomas
OL,14,FMair in her Batley and Spen
OL,15,Fconstituency on 16 June 2016.
OL,17,FSandra Major and Fazila Aswat, who
OL,18,Fwere the MP's assistants at the time,
OL,19,Fwere with her when she was attacked in
OL,20,FMarket Street, in daylight, before a
OL,21,Fconstituency surgery.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
