FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1781887673
OL,3,CJo Cox told friends 'let him hurt me'
OL,4,Cas they tried to stop killer
OL,6,FSpeaking together for the first time
OL,7,Fsince the incident - ahead of the 10th
OL,8,Fanniversary of Mrs Cox's death - they
OL,9,Frecalled how they were getting out of
OL,10,Fa car when Mair shot the MP.
OL,12,FMs Aswat said: "I think it probably
OL,13,Ftook me a minute to register what was
OL,14,Factually going on.... initially, I
OL,15,Fjust thought she'd fallen over.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1781887673
OL,3,CJo Cox told friends 'let him hurt me'
OL,4,Cas they tried to stop killer
OL,6,F"And then Sandra started screaming,
OL,7,Fand then I saw him standing over her
OL,8,Fwith a gun and a knife in his hand...
OL,9,FAt that point she was alive and all I
OL,10,Fcould think about was her children and
OL,11,FI kept just kept saying, 'Jo, you just
OL,12,Fneed to stay with me'. But
OL,13,Funfortunately he continued and he was
OL,14,Fdetermined to kill her."
OL,16,FMs Major added: "We started hitting
OL,17,Fhim with our handbags, because what
OL,18,Felse do you do?
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1781887673
OL,3,CJo Cox told friends 'let him hurt me'
OL,4,Cas they tried to stop killer
OL,6,F"And then Jo said to to us, 'Get away,
OL,7,Fyou two get away. Let him hurt me, not
OL,8,Fyou'."
OL,10,FMs Aswat said Mrs Cox's last words to
OL,11,Fher were "Fazila, I'm hurt".
OL,13,F"She died in my arms after that," she
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1781887673
OL,3,CJo Cox told friends 'let him hurt me'
OL,4,Cas they tried to stop killer
OL,6,FMs Major added: "One of the worst
OL,7,Fthings for me was Jo's mum and dad
OL,8,Fcame running up the road, and Jean,
OL,9,FJo's mum, flung her arms round me and
OL,10,Fsaid, 'please tell me she's all right,
OL,11,FSandra. Please tell me she's all
OL,12,Fright'.
OL,14,F"I just said, 'they're working on her.
OL,15,FYou need to get there as quickly as
OL,16,Fyou can'.
OL,18,F"As a mother, saying that to another
OL,19,Fmother - and I knew that her child had
OL,20,Fgone - was one of the hardest things
OL,21,Fthat I've ever done."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
