PN,33810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1781887673
OL,3,CJo Cox told friends 'let him hurt me'
OL,4,Cas they tried to stop killer
OL,6,FMs Major added: "Her legacy is still
OL,7,Fthere and there are so many people who
OL,8,Fare trying to keep that message alive.
OL,9,FWe will never forget her - and just be
OL,10,Fkind and full of love like Jo was."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/10
